				<div style="font-style:italic">Is there any proof that she would have survived had she taken the transfusion? Neither article linked says that if they had given her blood she would have lived. Yes, it's very sad, and maybe (even probably) it could have been avoided - but sometimes people die from childbirth - it happens.</div>
			
